group.name: Brussels Nutrition and Weight Loss Meetup

description:
You are warmly invited to join us at this new and inspirational meet up our aim is to start you on a journey of "weightloss and well being". 


Inspirations and facts on how to make the changes you want to make in your health and well being.  


Lets meet and start the "Change process".

This evening is for those who want to improve their weight (loss) or take control of their well being. 

We will support those who are serious through the whole process.
name: Lets get started...
